n's tennis\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Federerhas retired, while Nadal has struggled with injuries in recent years, with the 38-year-old's Olympic singles participationin doubt over a thigh issue.\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.758245990383886e-16, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Federerhas\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 346}, {\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \"the 38-year-old's Olympic singles participationin\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"a thigh issue\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic, though, is still very much near the top of the sport - and came close to landing this year's Wimbledon title - only losing out toCarlos Alcarazin the final.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Djokovic\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 495}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Wimbledon title\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"Alcarazin\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Serbian won three of the four Grand Slam tournaments in 2023 and despite a dip in form this season, he is adamant he hasno plans to hang up his racketat all.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.7214164799073621, \"rank\": 0.34569599764304176, \"text\": \"Serbian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http: