/resource/Matthew_Ebden\"}, {\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.758245990383886e-16, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.9776423337479124, \"rank\": 0.022359719571527395, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"retirement\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic singles first-round match\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"a potentialblockbuster\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even though I know a lot of people would love me to retire so this era is done.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"this era\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think as long as there is at least one of us left competing, the era is still going.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"the era\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Of course there is a change of generations.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a change\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"generations\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have Alcaraz and [Jannik] Sinner, currently they are our two best players in the world, deservedly.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1338, \"e